data.description: Fabulous 4 bedroom home in Rivendale Pointe! This quiet neighborhood is minutes from Lake Lewisville and so many great Frisco restaurants and shopping amenities. Enjoy community features including a clubhouse, community pool and playground. Lovely drive up and pristine interior!  Soaring ceilings and big windows overlooking backyard with green space beyond that. Open floor plan provides tons of natural light for both downstairs and up, making both living areas, light filled and cozy. Living room with gas fireplace overlooks backyard and opens to the eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar, granite counters, stainless steel appliances including built-in microwave and pantry.  Primary bedroom suite has garden tub, separate shower and walk in closet! Upstairs has spacious game room perfect for kids, 3 bedrms and full bath. Awesome backyard with turf putting green, covered patio is perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Fantastic home, move in ready! Back on market no fault of home or seller.
